This project demonstrates end-to-end data analysis using Microsoft Excel, focusing on business performance insights through pivot tables, KPIs, and an interactive dashboard.

The goal of the project is to analyze sales, profit, discounts, customer segments, and delivery performance and present insights in a clear, decision-ready format.

