ðŸ“ˆ Analysis Covered

The Excel analysis answers the following business questions:

Which product categories generate the highest sales and profit?

Which regions are most profitable?

Which sub-categories are loss-making?

How do discounts affect average profit?

How do different customer segments perform?

Which shipping modes take the longest to deliver orders?

